  "text": [
    "<strong dir=\"rtl\">לַח</strong> m. (b. h.;  לחח <i>to be sticky, sappy, fresh</i>) <i>moist, green, fresh; liquid</i>; opp. <a dir=\"rtl\" class=\"refLink\" href=\"/Jastrow,_יָבֵשׁ I.1\" data-ref=\"Jastrow, יָבֵשׁ I 1\">יבש</a>. <a class=\"refLink\" href=\"/Mishnah_Demai.2.3\" data-ref=\"Mishnah Demai 2:3\">Dem. II, 3</a> <span dir=\"rtl\">לח ויבש</span> either fresh or dried fruits. <a class=\"refLink\" href=\"/Mishnah_Demai.2.5\" data-ref=\"Mishnah Demai 2:5\">Ib. 5</a> <span dir=\"rtl\">ובלח דינר</span> in selling fresh fruits (or liquids), a denar’s worth is wholesale; Y. ib. II, end, 23ᵃ <span dir=\"rtl\">נתנו דמים ללח וכ׳</span> for fresh fruit they adopt the standard of value, for dried that of quantity (cmp. <a dir=\"rtl\" class=\"refLink\" href=\"/Jastrow,_לוּמָּא.1\" data-ref=\"Jastrow, לוּמָּא 1\">לוּמָּא</a>); <a class=\"refLink\" href=\"/Tosefta_Demai.3.12\" data-ref=\"Tosefta Demai 3:12\">Tosef. ib. III, 12</a> <span dir=\"rtl\">ובלח הין</span> and for <i>liquids</i> the standard is a <i>Hin</i>. <a class=\"refLink\" href=\"/Bereishit_Rabbah.79.7\" data-ref=\"Bereishit Rabbah 79:7\">Gen. R. s. 79</a>, beg. (play on <span dir=\"rtl\">כלח</span>, <a class=\"refLink\" href=\"/Job.5.26\" data-ref=\"Job 5:26\">Job V, 26</a>) <span dir=\"rtl\">תבא לח וכ׳</span> thou shalt die in the possession of vigor (cmp. <a class=\"refLink\" href=\"/Deuteronomy.34.7\" data-ref=\"Deuteronomy 34:7\">Deut. XXXIV, 7</a>); a. fr.—<i>Fem</i>. <a dir=\"rtl\" class=\"refLink\" href=\"/Jastrow,_לֵחָה.1\" data-ref=\"Jastrow, לֵחָה 1\">לַחָה</a>. <a class=\"refLink\" href=\"/Shabbat.49a.4\" data-ref=\"Shabbat 49a:4\">Sabb. 49ᵃ</a> <span dir=\"rtl\">כסות ל׳</span> a moist garment; a. fr.—Pl. <span dir=\"rtl\">לַחִים</span>, <span dir=\"rtl\">לַחִין</span>; <span dir=\"rtl\">לַחוֹת</span>. Ib. <span dir=\"rtl\">ל׳ מחמת עצמן וכ׳</span> naturally moist, <span dir=\"rtl\">ל׳ מחמת דבר אחר</span> moist through some incident. Y. Ber. I, 2ᶜ bot. <span dir=\"rtl\">ל׳ היו שמים וכ׳</span> the heavens were liquid …, and on the second day they congealed (v. <a dir=\"rtl\" class=\"refLink\" href=\"/Jastrow,_גָּלַד.1\" data-ref=\"Jastrow, גָּלַד 1\">גָּלַד</a>); <a class=\"refLink\" href=\"/Bereishit_Rabbah.4.7\" data-ref=\"Bereishit Rabbah 4:7\">Gen. R. s. 4</a>, beg. <span dir=\"rtl\">ל׳ היו מעשיהם</span> (corr. acc.); a. fr.—V. <a dir=\"rtl\" class=\"refLink\" href=\"/Jastrow,_לֵחָה.1\" data-ref=\"Jastrow, לֵחָה 1\">לֵחָה</a>."
  ],
